# ğŸ” SmartSys Analyzer

**SmartSys Analyzer** is a powerful and stylish Python system monitoring toolkit. It tracks CPU, memory, and disk usage with configurable thresholds, colorful logging, and intelligent alerts â€” built with â¤ï¸ for developers, sysadmins, and enthusiasts.

