## âœ¨ Features

- âœ… Configurable resource thresholds (CPU, Memory, Disk)
- âœ… Pydantic-based validation models
- âœ… Colored terminal logs (via Colorama + Rich)
- âœ… JSON config loader and saver
- âœ… Cross-platform OS detection
- âœ… Internet connectivity checker
- âœ… Alert system (text + optional sound)
- âœ… Language selection (EN, ID, ZH-Hans, AR)
- âœ… Retry decorators and smart utilities
- âœ… Fully PyPI-packaged and documented

